### create task
POST {{baseUrl}}task
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Task 0",
  "description": "Task 0 description"
}

### get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}task
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### get task by id
