Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### update task
PATCH {{baseUrl}}task/ccaf6b06-6f7c-42c5-9712-5539ae545b89
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "aaaaa": "Task 0 Updated",
  "isDone": true
}

